    • contains

      public boolean contains​(Location location)
      Grid cells are inclusive of their edges for containment. This means that a location exactly on the grid cell border is included.
      Specified by:
      contains in interface Outline
      Overrides:
      contains in class Rectangle
      Parameters:
      location - The location
      Returns:
      True if this rectangle contains the location (if the location is >= the lower left corner AND < the top right corner).
